children.name: When I click on register link
And I click on radio button against female
And I select day for DOB "11"

And I select year for DOB "1995"
And I enter email for registration
And I enter password for registration "pari@10"
And I enter confirm password for registration "pari@10"
And I click on register for registration
Then I should get registration completion message "Your registration completed"
